details.message:
`004.003.002 Asset_Tabs`
- Test checks the ability to create/update/delete data on every tab linked to assets. 
- Account: Add and remove "SMCT 002".
- Attachments: Add and remove an attachment.
- Associated Links: Add and remove a link.
- Attributes: Add and remove a new attribute.
- Events: Add and remove an event.
- Extra Failure Types: Add and remove extra failure type.
- Fixed Asset Data: Add more asset data.
- Operator Log: Add and remove a log.
- Warranties: Add and remove a warranty.
- The following tabs are omitted since they are read-only: Condition, Cost Summary, Downtime History, Failure History, Failure Profile, Financial Transactions, Maintenance Strategy Calendar Triggers, Maintenance Strategy Op Tolerance Triggers, Maintenance Strategy Runtime Triggers, Performance History, and Work History.
